# 2️⃣ Explain

## 📌 App

An App in Salesforce is a collection of related tabs, objects, and tools designed for a specific business purpose.

## 📌 Object

An Object is a database table used to store information in Salesforce. It contains records and fields.

## 📌 Tab

A Tab is used to access objects, reports, dashboards, and applications easily within Salesforce.

