# 3️⃣ Difference: Configuration vs Coding

| Configuration | Coding |
|---|---|
| Click-based development | Programming-based development |
| No coding knowledge required | Requires programming knowledge |
| Faster and easier | More flexible and advanced |
| Uses tools like Flows and Validation Rules | Uses Apex and Lightning Components |

